('Black & Tan','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/rwpswp1454511017.jpg','Fill pint glass half full with Bass. Next pour Guiness over a spoon slowly until glass is full. If done correctly the Guiness will stay on top and the Bass on bottom hence the name Black & Tan.'),
